    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pit of Gerstan is a roguelite dungeoneering action game. Hack, slash, throw and blast your way through hordes of enemies and bosses, as you collect various items, upgrades and weapons to create the ultimate dungeon-clearing hero. Build your own unique hero and playstyle while facing many enemies, hazards, secrets and bosses within the Pit of Gerstan! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244840/extras/0f09e0452b8aac7f1eee375e45f6661f.poster.avif?t=1731687595\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244840/extras/0f09e0452b8aac7f1eee375e45f6661f.webm?t=1731687595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244840/extras/0f09e0452b8aac7f1eee375e45f6661f.mp4?t=1731687595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features of the Demo</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first 2 Levels - mostly complete</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First 2 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >28+ weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ upgrades</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features Planned for Full Release</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally Generated Dungeons with many Secrets and Hazards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable Characters with varied properties</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging Bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+ Weapons with their own properties and special abilities </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200 Unique Upgrades to craft your own Playstyle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Metaprogression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seed System</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More details to come.</p>",
